                        class="font-bold uppercase text-[32px] leading-[35px] lg:leading-[65px] lg:text-[70px] text-center pt-10 lg:pt-14 lg:w-4/5 mx-auto"
                    >
                        <span class="text-white"
                            >MAKING YOU STAND OUT AT </span
                        ><span class="text-light-green">
                            EVENTS & EXHIBITIONS</span
