                    </h1>

                    <p
                        class="text-white font-medium text-[22px] leading-[30px] text-center pt-10 lg:pt-[60px] lg:w-[57%] lg:px-10"
                    >
                        From eye-catching roller banners to impactful pop-up
                        displays, Brand Works offers a complete suite of
                        marketing materials designed to make your stand and
                        events the stars of the show.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Anchored link buttons -->
                <div
                    class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-9 gap-y-6 pt-7 justify-center relative w-full lg:w-3/4 mx-auto"
                >
                    <a href="#fabric-displays" class="outline-button"
