                        class="font-bold uppercase text-[32px] leading-[35px] lg:leading-[65px] lg:text-[70px] text-white"
                    >
                        FABRIC DISPLAYS
                    </h2>

                    <h3
                        class="font-medium text-[32px] leading-[35px] pt-8 lg:pt-11 text-light-green"
                    >
                        Ditch the Bulk, Embrace the Impact: Fabric Displays
                        for a Winning Exhibition Presence.
                    </h3>

                    <p class="text-white pt-10">
                        Say goodbye to bulky pop-up booths and flimsy banner
                        stands! Brand Works offers lightweight, portable
                        fabric displays that are the future of impactful
                        exhibition experiences. Imagine tossing out the
                        backaches and wrestling matches with heavy
                        components. Fabric displays are crafted from
                        high-quality, wrinkle-resistant fabric, making them
                        a breeze to transport and set up. Simply pack your
                        display in a convenient carrying case and you're
                        ready to wow!<br /><br />
                        But portability isn't the only benefit. Our
                        state-of-the-art printing process ensures vibrant
                        colors and crisp graphics that grab attention and
                        leave a lasting impression. Fabric displays offer a
                        seamless, professional look that elevates your brand
                        presence and sets you apart from the crowd.<br /><br />
                        We offer a wide range of fabric display options to
                        suit your specific needs and space limitations. From
                        pop-up booths and tension fabric walls to hanging
                        banners and table throws, the versatility of fabric
                        displays is unmatched.
                    </p>

                    <div class="hidden lg:block pt-10">
                        <a
                            href="{{ site.url }}/contact-us"
                            target="_self"
                            class="solid-button-tall max-w-max"
                        >
                            START YOUR PROJECT
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Two column image and text - image right -->
    <section
        class="bg-gradient-to-b from-dark-green from-0 via-dark-green via-70% to-white to-100% pb-10 lg:pb-20"
