                    >
                        BOLLARD COVERS
                    </h2>

                    <h3
                        class="font-medium text-[32px] leading-[35px] pt-8 lg:pt-11 text-dark-green"
                    >
                        Transform Everyday Objects into Mini Billboards:
                        Branded Bollard Covers
                    </h3>

                    <p class="pt-10">
                        Those ubiquitous bollards lining streets and
                        walkways? They can be more than just safety
                        barriers. At Brand Works, we transform them into
                        silent brand ambassadors with our custom-printed
                        bollard covers.<br /><br />
                        Imagine turning these everyday objects into
                        eye-catching mini billboards. Our durable,
                        weather-resistant covers are a cost-effective way to
                        boost brand awareness and deliver targeted messages
                        directly to pedestrians. They're perfect for
                        promoting special offers, showcasing your logo, or
                        simply adding a splash of color to your storefront.
                        We offer a variety of sizes and printing options to
                        ensure a perfect fit and a message that resonates
                        with your audience. Let Brand Works help you turn
                        everyday objects into brand new marketing
                        opportunities.
                    </p>

                    <div class="hidden lg:block pt-10">
